 《博德之门 3》为卡拉赫添加了新结局https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-adds-new-endings-for-karlach-3491699?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=baldurs-gate-3-adds-new-卡拉赫结局Imogen DonovanThu, 31 Aug 2023 16:04:56 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3491699 <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p>以及任性朋友的威瑟斯衣柜</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-adds-new-endings-for-karlach-3491699">《博德之门 3》为卡拉赫添加了新结局，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-patch-2-karlach-ending-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a>今天（8 月 31 日）发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1086940/view/3656414378543586471" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第 2 补丁</a>，兑现了对玩家的承诺，即卡拉赫故事的结局将被改变。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/baldurs-gate-3-review-3481761">《博德之门 3》评论：必玩奇幻游戏大获好评</a></strong></li></ul><p>接下来将会有<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的剧透。在第三幕中，很明显提夫林野蛮人没有和平的结局，这种悲惨的现实让许多人心碎。团队对粉丝的反应做出了回应，并保证<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-is-changing-its-most-controversial-ending-3490895">该角色将获得“火热”和“辛酸”的替代结局</a>。</p><p>拉里安工作室没有说明补丁 2 中添加的“附加场景”包含哪些内容，但与卡拉赫选择前往阿弗纳斯的时间有关。</p><p>此外，如果当“地狱之刃提出要和她一起去地狱时，卡拉克在玩家队伍中，你现在可以决定是和他们一起去，单独和卡拉克一起去，还是让他们自己走”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3477707" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477707" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3477707" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character.jpg" alt="《博德之门 3》。图片来源：Larian Studios。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-Origin-Character-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477707" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》。图片来源：Larian Studios。</figcaption></figure><p>补丁 2 还解决了游戏文本中的拼写错误等不一致问题，并且游戏现在允许玩家在角色进步并解锁新能力时跳过升级动画。</p><p> <em>《博德之门 3》</em>的本次更新重点关注了控制器兼容性和控制，例如径向菜单、平视显示器 (HUD)、工具提示、控制器用户界面的总体视觉改进以及关于按压和操作的更清晰说明。保持命令。</p><p>另一个主要新增内容是威瑟斯任性朋友的衣橱功能，这是角色可以在改变玩家职业和复活死去同伴的同时完成的一项新任务。</p><p> “威瑟斯听过塔夫斯的故事，他们要求朋友们一起度过一个下午的冒险，希望回到没有朋友陪伴的独行冒险家的生活方式，”团队解释道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3476247" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476247" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3476247" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-does-not-allow-preloading-of-122GB-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476247" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> “有了这个木制品奇迹，你现在可以解雇合作党成员，并让你的同伴重新加入。然而，Withers 的解决方案仅适用于定制 Tav，因此不要将 Gale 扔进橱柜（尽管我们确信它放在那里很舒服），”Larian Studios 说道。</p><p>在其他地方，开发者分享说即将到来的更新之一将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-characters-can-get-makeovers-soon-3483227">允许玩家改变他们的自定义角色的外观</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-adds-new-endings-for-karlach-3491699">《博德之门 3》为卡拉赫添加了新结局，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
