 《哈利·波特》女演员金妮·韦斯莱对“缩减”银幕时间感到“失望” https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-ginny-weasley-actress-disappointed-with-chopped-down-screen-time-3491656?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=harry-potter-ginny-韦斯莱女演员对银幕时间被缩短感到失望Chris EdwardsThu, 31 Aug 2023 15:14:09 +0000 Film NewsNewsHarry Potter https://www.nme.com/?p=3491656 <p><img width="2030" height="1392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright.jpg 2030w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-400x274.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-800x549.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-696x477.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-1392x955.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-1068x732.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2030px) 100vw, 2030px" /></p><p> “这让我感到有点焦虑或沮丧”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-ginny-weasley-actress-disappointed-with-chopped-down-screen-time-3491656">《哈利·波特》后的女演员金妮·韦斯莱对“缩减”银幕时间感到“失望”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2030" height="1392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright.jpg 2030w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-400x274.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-800x549.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-696x477.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-1392x955.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Bonnie-Wright-1068x732.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2030px) 100vw, 2030px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/harry-potter"><em>《哈利·波特》</em></a>主演邦妮·赖特表示，她对自己在电影中“被削减”的放映时间感到“失望”。</p><p>这位演员在这部八部电影的传奇故事中扮演金妮·韦斯莱，从罗恩胆怯的妹妹成长为自信的年轻女巫，并最终成为丹尼尔·雷德克里夫饰演的哈利·波特的妻子。</p><p>然而，在迈克尔·罗森鲍姆 (Michael Rosenbaum) 的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KqOW45wD2a8&amp;pp=ygUfaW5zaWRlIG9mIHlvdSBtaWNoYWVsIHJvc2VuYmF1bQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Inside of You</em> 》播客</a>中露面时，赖特表示，如果编剧们更贴近 JK 罗琳的书，金妮的角色发展可能会有更多。</p><p>在聊天中，赖特解释了她在扮演金妮时感到焦虑和沮丧，担心如果角色没有得到公正的对待，粉丝会做出负面反应。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="邦妮·赖特：金妮·韦斯莱的成长、哈利·波特的下一代和分享脆弱性" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KqOW45wD2a8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “例如，我确实感到人们对表演和做最好的事情感到焦虑，就像我的角色所塑造的那样，”她说。 “就像，‘天哪，我会公正地对待这个人们喜爱的角色吗？’</p><p> “所以这总是很难做到，尤其是当每个角色的很多场景不可避免地从书中被删减到电影中时。所以你在电影中并没有太多可展示的东西。”</p><p>她补充道：“有时这有点令人失望，因为角色的某些部分没有表现出来，因为没有场景可以做到这一点，”她继续道。 “我想这让我感到有点焦虑或沮丧。” </p><figure id="attachment_2564394" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2564394" style="width: 2048px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2564394" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family.jpg" alt="哈利·波特的韦斯莱一家" width="2048" height="1366" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family.jpg 2048w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/weasley-family-1068x712.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2564394" class="wp-caption-text"> 《哈利·波特》中的弗雷德、金妮、乔治和罗恩·韦斯莱。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>赖特接着说，有“一百万高管”负责剧本和改编书籍，很难对她的放映时间提出任何担忧。然而，她最终接受了事实：这超出了她的控制范围。</p><p> “当粉丝们确实表达了这种失望时，他们的方式就像是，‘我们知道那不是你。我们只是想要更多的你’，”她说。 “这对每个角色来说都是一样的。要是能拍成五个小时的电影就好了。”</p><p>巧合的是，粉丝们可能很快就会花更多的时间与金妮在一起，因为麦克斯（以前的 HBO Max）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-tv-series-officially-confirmed-at-hbo-3429311">目前正在制作一部<em>哈利·波特</em>电视剧</a>，并有望忠实地改编原著。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-ginny-weasley-actress-disappointed-with-chopped-down-screen-time-3491656">《哈利·波特》后的女演员金妮·韦斯莱对“缩减”银幕时间感到“失望”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 反思 2008 年《名利场》封面引发的“令人不安”的争议https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-reflects-on-upsetting-controversy-around-2008-vanity-fair-cover-3491659?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=miley-cyrus-reflects- 2008 年《名利场》封面上令人不安的争议Anagricel DuranThu, 31 Aug 2023 15:10:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3491659 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 4 月 23 日，麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 身着 Versace 出席在比佛利山庄酒店举行的《Daily Front Row》第七届年度时尚洛杉矶颁奖典礼。图片来源：Stefanie Keenan/Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我的形象与我所熟知的泡泡糖流行歌星完全相反，这就是如此令人沮丧的地方”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-reflects-on-upsetting-controversy-around-2008-vanity-fair-cover-3491659">麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 反思 2008 年《名利场》封面的“令人不安”的争议，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 4 月 23 日，麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus) 身着 Versace 出席在比佛利山庄酒店举行的《Daily Front Row》第七届年度时尚洛杉矶颁奖典礼。图片来源：Stefanie Keenan/Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Miley-Cyrus-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus)</a>反思了围绕她<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/culture/2008/06/miley200806" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2008 年<em>《名利场》</em>封面</a>引发的“令人不安”的争议。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/miley-cyrus-endless-summer-vacation-review-lyrics-tracklist-3409627">麦莉·赛勒斯 - 《无尽的暑假》评论：强有力的权力回收</a></strong></li></ul><p>赛勒斯在最近一集中的“曾经年轻”TikTok 系列中讨论了杂志封面，在该系列中，她回顾了整个职业生涯的重要时刻，赛勒斯反思了她是多么享受拍摄照片的过程。</p><p> “每个人都知道这张照片的争议，但他们并不真正了解幕后花絮，而幕后花絮总是更有意义，”这位歌手在谈到封面照片时说道，当时 15 岁的赛勒斯身穿白色衣服。涂有红色口红的床单，由著名摄影师安妮·莱博维茨拍摄。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@mileycyrus/video/7273124079849180446" data-video-id="7273124079849180446" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section> <a target="_blank" title="@麦莉赛勒斯" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@mileycyrus?refer=embed">@麦莉赛勒斯</a></p><p>曾经年轻（系列）-第15部分</p><p><a target="_blank" title="♬ 曾经年轻 - 麦莉·赛勒斯" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/Used-To-Be-Young-7270927725950076930?refer=embed">♬ 曾经年轻 – 麦莉·赛勒斯</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> 她继续说：“我的妹妹诺亚（赛勒斯）坐在安妮的腿上，实际上按下了相机的按钮拍照，”她说。 “我的家人都在片场，这是我第一次涂红色口红。为我化妆的帕蒂·杜布罗夫 (Pati Dubroff) 认为，这将是另一个将我与汉娜·蒙塔娜 (Hannah Montana) 区分开来的因素。”</p><p>赛勒斯随后解释说，这张照片背后的争议在于，封面上的她与她当时所扮演的儿童友好型迪士尼角色汉娜·蒙塔娜截然相反。</p><p> “我的形象与我所熟知的泡泡糖流行歌星完全相反，这就是令人沮丧的地方，”她说。 “但是，现在回想起来，那些人的选择真的非常非常明智。”</p><p> 2008 年封面首次发布时，赛勒斯发表声明，为拍摄照片道歉。 “我参加了一次应该是‘艺术’的照片拍摄，现在看到这些照片、读到这个故事，我感到非常尴尬，”她当时在一份声明中说道。 “我从来没有想过发生这样的事情，我向我非常关心的粉丝道歉。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwnMJL3utaf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72